{"tid":1855918,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★人民銀行等部委推30項措施 避免非理性情緒對金融市場的影響","createTime":"2020-02-01T10:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T07:03:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"374ed67d9f30b0c373e9200d3c4f4769589ecbc3","tid":1855918,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:31:51.000Z","msg":"內地5個部委推出30項措施，強化金融支持防控疫情，以及避免非理性情緒對金融市場的影響。<br />\n<br />\n人民銀行、財政部及證監會等5個部委推出的措施，包括保持資金流動性合理充裕，通過公開市場操作等多種貨幣政策工具，提供充足流動性，維護貨幣市場利率平穩運行；同時加大對疫情防控相關領域的信貸支持力度，並為受疫情影響較大的地區、行業和企業，提供差異化優惠的金融服務，例如批發零售、住宿餐飲、物流運輸、文化旅遊等行業，特別是小微企業。同時，適當放寬資本市場相關業務辦理時限，以至減免疫情嚴重地區公司上市等部分費用等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506064-20200201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506064-20200201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5ItUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=cb7693b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506064-20200201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0793fa8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506064-20200201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"29ca6e51215da446f1b0d5ee2f8242c348f9fa7c","tid":1855918,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:32:10.000Z","msg":"drop to 0?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b139df646090af5222b32490de26f907980c729","tid":1855918,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:32:38.000Z","msg":"有救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" cla